scene.message:
Elly: The Snow Queen is{nl}
the embodiment of Tomomi's{nl}
darker side.{waitkey}{clearbox}By holding up the "Demon's{nl}
Mirror" reflecting all evil,{nl}
Tomomi{wait_fr:30}—the Snow Queen—{waitkey}{clearbox}saw for herself just how{nl}
desolate her own heart{nl}
had become.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: The Snow Queen{nl}
symbolizes the dark part{nl}
that lay in Tomomi's heart.{waitkey}{clearbox}By holding up the "Demon's{nl}
Mirror" reflecting all evil,{nl}
Tomomi{wait_fr:30}—the Snow Queen—{waitkey}{clearbox}saw just how tainted{nl}
her own heart had{nl}
become.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: I see!{waitkey}Seeing her own ugly self{nl}
in the mirror, Tomomi{nl}
came to her senses.{waitkey}{clearbox}So her Persona, the Night{nl}
Queen, lost its place and{nl}
began to rampage, huh.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Nice explaining.{waitkey}{clearbox}Finally even I've got{nl}
the gist of it.{waitkey}So basically{waitkey}{clearbox}if we don't beat the Night{nl}
Whatsit, we can't go home{nl}
or take a nice hot bath!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Hmm. So in the end{nl}
we've still gotta beat the{nl}
Night Whatsit too, huh.{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Saeko: You kids...{nl}
You've grown so dependable{nl}
while I wasn't watching.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: We only got this far{nl}
because everyone was here{nl}
for me.{waitkey}Ayase alone could never{nl}
have...{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Yeah.{nl}
Thanks to these guys{wait_fr:30}...{nl}
well...{wait_fr:30}{nl}
I can't say it well, but{waitkey}{clearbox}for the first time I feel{nl}
I understand what it{nl}
means to be alive.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Sh-{wait_fr:30}shut up!{waitkey}Let's go, {ctl0f:1}!{waitkey}{clearbox}Night Queen or whatever,{nl}
with this crew here we've{nl}
got nothing to fear!{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Saeko: Heh...{waitkey}{ctl0f:1}!{nl}
I'm counting on you to{nl}
look after everyone!!{waitkey}{ret}

Tomomi: Ms. Saeko...{wait_fr:30}{nl}
Everyone{wait_fr:30}... thank you.{waitkey}{clearbox}Thanks to all of you,{nl}
I was able to reclaim{nl}
my human heart.{waitkey}{clearbox}The self in the mirror,{wait_fr:30}{nl}
my own heart,{wait_fr:30}{nl}
was too ugly to face...{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: It's not just you,{nl}
Tomomi.{waitkey}{clearbox}Anyone who stands before{nl}
that mirror is bound{nl}
to look ugly.{waitkey}{clearbox}People with truly pure{nl}
hearts are a rare thing{nl}
indeed.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Me, on the other hand,{nl}
I'm innocent as a young girl,{nl}
pure as an angel{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...{waitkey}{clearbox}...Sorry.{waitkey}{ret}

Tomomi: The way you are now,{nl}
you won't look like{nl}
monsters at all...{waitkey}{clearbox}Oh, that's right!{waitkey}You should keep the "Demon's{nl}
Mirror" with you from now on.{waitkey}{clearbox}I'm sure it will protect{nl}
you all from misfortune.{waitkey}{clearbox}A mirror's hard to carry{nl}
as it is, so...{waitkey}{ret}

Tomomi: Also, I'm not sure{nl}
it'll be of any help, but...{waitkey}{clearbox}The costumes worn by past{nl}
"Snow Queen" leads should{nl}
be in the gym storeroom.{waitkey}{clearbox}They were set near the box{nl}
to strengthen the seal on{nl}
the "Snow Queen's Mask."{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Huh, good to know.{waitkey}{clearbox}I don't know where in this{nl}
Ice Castle the storeroom is,{nl}
but it's worth a look.{waitkey}{ret}

Tomomi: Ah...{wait_fr:30} If only{nl}
I'd met you all sooner...{waitkey}{clearbox}So no second or third selves{nl}
are ever born, I'll watch{nl}
over the school from heaven{nl}
with the Queens before me.{waitkey}Thank you all.{waitkey}{ret}
